</quote>
<pc>」</pc>行<measure quantity="60" unit="LIs">
<num value="60">六十</num>里</measure>
<pc>，</pc>夜<pc>，</pc>至張柴村<pc>，</pc>盡殺其戍卒及烽子<pc>。</pc>據其柵<pc>，</pc>命士卒少休<pc>，</pc>食干□<pc>，</pc>整羈靮<pc>，</pc>留義成軍<measure quantity="500" unit="people">
<num value="500">五百</num>人</measure>鎮之<pc>，</pc>以斷朗山救兵<pc>。</pc>命丁士良將<measure quantity="500" unit="people">
<num value="500">五百</num>人</measure>斷洄曲及諸道橋樑<pc>，</pc>復夜引兵出門<pc>。</pc>諸將請所之<pc>，</pc>愬曰<pc>：</pc>
<pc>「</pc>
<quote>入<placeName>蔡州</placeName>取吳元濟<pc>！</pc>
